{"tid":1875093,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救！）有隻三個月大嘅唐狗女被差啲俾送中！急要主人！","createTime":"2020-02-11T14:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T17:26:53.000Z","uid":327423,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"85a0216e78f40b86bb3ecd887b1d0c1e9b1d7767","tid":1875093,"uid":327423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"隻狗bb係某個親戚唔知係邊度執返嚟嘅，話無人領養就會攞返大陸，我同朋友截住咗但無人可以養到佢，而家急需主人！<br />\n<br />\n***********************************************<br />\n<br />\nHello , 我個名叫湯圓！係隻唐狗女！今年3個月大！醫生話我無病無痛，嚟緊會打第一次針啦，我好活潑好得意，仲好叻添！我學咗幾日就識得去廁所啦，又識得sit，我唔會吠陌生人仲好鍾意同人玩㗎！如果有興趣嘅好心人願意，我可以陪住你，我想搵個負責任嘅主人，做你屋企嘅開心果！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecN2mL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecN2mL0.jpg&h=dedf5991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣可以聯絡我！或者幫手大大力share！"},{"pid":"395095a0cf1872503c9b8ab3e0da9d0eb4f4c72b","tid":1875093,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52db59481f08e0d8df519ff2bd3d02a1ae60a647","tid":1875093,"uid":61918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"122ea9d7766becfada1c8342c94561fe5af581b5","tid":1875093,"uid":315647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b1c2dadbd4f9db92c0ef648ac9d2f9fbdfd1fcd","tid":1875093,"uid":5568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"572c4b6bb7cfd020545083116a05016f573b5383","tid":1875093,"uid":315647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"好得意！"},{"pid":"258f8db3d136470a4fc4e1cc4baa87f42ca4350e","tid":1875093,"uid":69846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"幫推 得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca270ed7fc0b69a72ca4b6e70306848d46a2efb","